N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4119.10 - Conspiracy

State Regulations

No person shall conspire, combine and confederate
together in any manner, regardless of where the said person may be located, for
the purpose of violating any of these rules nor shall they commit any act in
furtherance of the said purpose and plan. Notes
